      <title>Bookmark management with QOwnNotes and Web Companion browser extension</title>
      <link>http://www.qownnotes.org/Blog/Bookmark-management-with-QOwnNotes-and-Web-Companion-browser-extension</link>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;If you want to take a look at the first release of the&lt;b&gt;&amp;nbsp;bookmark management&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;capabilities of QOwnNotes and the&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://github.com/qownnotes/web-companion/" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Web Companion browser extension&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;install the latest release of the extension from the&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/qownnotes-web-companion/pkgkfnampapjbopomdpnkckbjdnpkbkp" target="_blank"&gt;Chrome Web Store&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;or the&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://addons.mozilla.org/firefox/addon/qownnotes-web-companion" target="_blank"&gt;Firefox Add-ons page&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Don't forget to update your installation of QOwnNotes as well!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;For more information about the &lt;b&gt;syntax&lt;/b&gt; of the &lt;b&gt;bookmark links&lt;/b&gt; and everything else please visit the&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.qownnotes.org/Knowledge-base/QOwnNotes-Web-Companion-browser-extension" target="_self"&gt;QOwnNotes Web Companion browser extension&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;knowledge page entry.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=""&gt;&lt;div class="content-view-embed"&gt;
    &lt;div class="class-image"&gt;
        &lt;div class="attribute-image"&gt;
            

    
        
    
