      <title>QOwnNotes Web Companion Chrome extension</title>
      <link>http://www.qownnotes.org/Blog/QOwnNotes-Web-Companion-Chrome-extension</link>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;In version 18.12.7 I added support for the new rudimentary&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://github.com/qownnotes/chrome-web-companion/" target="_blank"&gt;QOwnNotes Web Companion &lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="https://github.com/qownnotes/chrome-web-companion/" target="_blank"&gt;Chrome&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://github.com/qownnotes/chrome-web-companion/" target="_blank"&gt;extension&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;to add selected text as new note!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You can download the current release of the extension at&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://github.com/qownnotes/chrome-web-companion/releases/tag/18.12.0" target="_blank"&gt;QOwnNotes Chrome Web Companion 18.12.0&lt;/a&gt;, just drop the file into Chrome to install the extension.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Please head over to&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://github.com/pbek/QOwnNotes/issues/330" target="_blank"&gt;#330&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;to comment on the development process.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
