      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;QOwnNotes&lt;/b&gt; did get&amp;nbsp;some attention lately. It&amp;nbsp;got featured on &lt;a href="https://youtu.be/om6iJFnqpI8?t=13m54s" target="_blank"&gt;LINUX Unplugged podcast 231&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://twitter.com/ubuntu/status/951472292495876096" target="_blank"&gt;@ubuntu&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;and &lt;a href="https://twitter.com/snapcraftio/status/951109910410027010" target="_blank"&gt;@snapcraft&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Update: QOwnNotes was also mentioned in the&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://mintcast.org/2018/01/08/mintcast-279-looking-back-at-2017-predictions" target="_blank"&gt;mintCast epsisode 279&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;at minute 23:09.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://youtu.be/om6iJFnqpI8?t=13m54s" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;a href="https://youtu.be/om6iJFnqpI8?t=13m54s" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;img src="https://www.qownnotes.org/var/bekerle/storage/images/media/images/linux-unplugged-231/4741-1-eng-GB/LINUX-Unplugged-231_reference.jpg" alt=""
