    <item>
      <title>QOwnNotes now has scripting support</title>
      <link>http://www.qownnotes.org/Blog/QOwnNotes-now-has-scripting-support</link>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;QOwnNotes&lt;/b&gt; now&amp;nbsp;has &lt;b&gt;scripting support&lt;/b&gt; with &lt;b&gt;QML&lt;/b&gt; and &lt;b&gt;JavaScript&lt;/b&gt;!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;By using the power of the QQmlEngine and QML files with JavaScript you are now able to &lt;b&gt;script some new behavior&lt;/b&gt; into the application &lt;b&gt;yourself&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You will find a new&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;Scripting&amp;nbsp;tab&lt;/b&gt; in the settings dialog, where you can &lt;b&gt;add as many scripts&lt;/b&gt; to QOwnNotes &lt;b&gt;as you like&lt;/b&gt; (you can also disable them temporarily).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Currently you may need to restart QOwnNotes to let changes in a script take action.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;I prepared some&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href="https://github.com/pbek/QOwnNotes/tree/develop/doc/scripting" target="_blank"&gt;examples and documentation&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;to play around with.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If you need access to a certain functionality in QOwnNotes or have &lt;b&gt;questions or ideas&lt;/b&gt; please open an issue on the&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://github.com/pbek/QOwnNotes/issues" target="_blank"&gt;QOwnNotes issue page&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=""&gt;&lt;div class="content-view-embed"&gt;
    &lt;div class="class-image"&gt;
        &lt;div class="attribute-image"&gt;
            

    
        
    
                                                                                                                                            &lt;img src="https://www.qownnotes.org/var/bekerle/storage/images/qownnotes/frontpage-slider/qownnotes-scripting-with-qml-and-javascript/3866-1-eng-GB/QOwnNotes-scripting-with-QML-and-JavaScript_reference.png" width="600" height="518"  style="border: 0px solid ;" alt="Scripting support with QML and JavaScript" title="Scripting support with QML and JavaScript" /&gt;
            
    
    
            &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</description>
      <author>office+admin@bekerle.com (Patrizio Bekerle)</author>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">830bd8d62771e481b761505a5b2e2dbc</guid>
