&lt;b&gt;QOwnNotes&lt;/b&gt; uses the same &lt;b&gt;text files&lt;/b&gt; as the &lt;b&gt;ownCloud notes&lt;/b&gt; app.&lt;br /&gt;OwnNote uses HTML in the database.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Please read &lt;a href="https://www.qownnotes.org/Knowledge-base/Does-QOwnNotes-support-ownNote" target="_self"&gt;Does QOwnNotes support ownNote&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;for more information.&lt;/p&gt;
