      <title>Qt widget QMarkdownTextEdit now a separate project for developer's pleasure</title>
      <link>http://www.qownnotes.org/Blog/Qt-widget-QMarkdownTextEdit-now-a-separate-project-for-developer-s-pleasure</link>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;For the pleasure of you developers I extracted the markdown widget functionality out of QOwnNotes and made it a separate&amp;nbsp;Qt widget.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;It's name is &lt;b&gt;QMarkdownTextEdit&lt;/b&gt; and you'll find it on &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href="https://github.com/pbek/qmarkdowntextedit/" target="_blank"&gt;QMarkdownTextEdit on&amp;nbsp;GitHub&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="object-center"&gt;&lt;div class="content-view-embed"&gt;
    &lt;div class="class-image"&gt;
        &lt;div class="attribute-image"&gt;
            

    
        
    
                                                                                                                                            &lt;img src="https://www.qownnotes.org/var/bekerle/storage/images/media/images/qmarkdowntextedit-screenshot/3278-1-eng-GB/QMarkdownTextEdit-screenshot_large.png" width="360" height="298"  style="border: 0px solid ;" alt="QMarkdownTextEdit screenshot" title="QMarkdownTextEdit screenshot" /&gt;
            
    
    
            &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;a name="eztoc3298_1" id="eztoc3298_1"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Current features&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;

&lt;li&gt;markdown highlighting&lt;/li&gt;

&lt;li&gt;clickable links with Ctrl + Click&lt;/li&gt;

&lt;li&gt;block indent with Tab and Shift + Tab&lt;/li&gt;

&lt;li&gt;duplicate text with Ctrl + Alt + Down&lt;/li&gt;

&lt;li&gt;searching of text with Ctrl + F
&lt;ul&gt;

&lt;li&gt;jump between search results with Up and Down&lt;/li&gt;

&lt;li&gt;close search field with Escape&lt;/li&gt;

&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;

&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
